# Lean starter — grow this only as `git status` shows new machine-generated noise.
# Canonical reference: https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/Swift.gitignore

# Xcode per-user state (window layouts, breakpoints, snapshots). Lives inside the .xcodeproj;
# ignoring the xcuserdata/ directory already covers the .xcuserstate file nested inside it.
xcuserdata/

# macOS Finder metadata
.DS_Store

# Build artifacts (archives, exports, notarization zips)
build/